{"TopicId":173329,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Ditching problems.","CreatedByName":"Lego_Prodigy","CreatedById":187421,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T01:04:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Lego_Prodigy","CreatedById":187421,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T01:04:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo at some point or another, your mission goes south and you are gonna crash soon. Out of options, you decide to bail out, but realize you can\u0027t bail more than one pilot at a time via EVA. or this this not true? Please tell me if I can EVA both pilots at once, as I tend to use the MK2 parts most, which has two pilots.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T01:21:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, if you are a pure stock player, you better work on your clicking finger speed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, build a launch escape system into the Abort action group.\u00A0 For planes, you can add a decoupler and some chutes to save the pod.\u00A0 Of course, there isn\u0027t a stock mk2 decoupler, the mk2 exapnsion pack does have them though.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how well EVA chutes (the mod) works with the new chutes in 1.4, but there is a auto eject module you can attach to all your inhabited modules and it will eject the kerbals fairly quickly.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/148345-141-eva-parachutes-ejection-seats-with-sound-multiple-parachutes/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/148345-141-eva-parachutes-ejection-seats-with-sound-multiple-parachutes/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-01T01:22:06Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2018 01:22  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aegolius13","CreatedById":165625,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T01:24:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you using the \u0022[\u0022 or \u0022]\u0022 keys to cycle between the Kerbal and ship?\u00A0 That definitely saves some time versus switching via map mode or whatnot.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T05:26:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, you can easily bail out multiple krew members. There are a lot of little details that can mess you up, but in general it works just fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you bail them out at over 550 m/s in the low atmosphere, they are likely to spaghettify and die. If you take so long to bail out the second one that they end up more than about 22km apart, one of them will get terminated. Or if you take so long to bail out the second one that his ship hits the ground and explodes, he won\u0027t make it either (surprise!).\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo yeah:\u00A0EVA the first, space to let go, [ to refocus the ship, wait for the static to clear, EVA the second, hit space to let go, open the PAW, activate the parachute, hit [ again to focus the first kerbal, open his PAW, activate his\u00A0parachute, and you\u0027re done! But if they are more than 2.2km apart, that final [ won\u0027t work, and either you will have to wait for them to get closer or use map mode to switch focus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRepeat if you have more than two in your ship. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u00221\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-01T05:28:52Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2018 05:28  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by bewing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T06:58:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u2018P\u2019 to activate chutes after EVA saves a lot of time in emergency bailouts \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T07:00:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh. True. All those keys to memorize is too much for my po\u0027 widdle brain. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u00221\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T15:43:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223341304\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522565924\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151713\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fourfa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, fourfa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u2018P\u2019 to activate chutes after EVA saves a lot of time in emergency bailouts \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223341305\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522566053\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh. True. All those keys to memorize is too much for my po\u0027 widdle brain. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat particular key is easy to remember, because it\u0027s what the kerbal is probably doing in his suit as he tries to remember how to activate the parachute.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lego_Prodigy","CreatedById":187421,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T16:12:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo how do I bail out both pilots with EVA chutes?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T16:20:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223341676\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522599138\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187421\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lego_Prodigy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Lego_Prodigy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo how do I bail out both pilots with EVA chutes?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame process that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154251-bewing/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022154251\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154251-bewing/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@bewing\u003C/a\u003E describes above:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nEVA pilot #1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSpace bar to let go of ladder\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n] key to switch back to ship\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEVA pilot #2\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSpace bar to let go of ladder\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nP key to activate parachute\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHit ] key until you\u0027re focused back on pilot #1 again\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nP key to activate parachute.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lego_Prodigy","CreatedById":187421,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T16:21:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOH! thanks man! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0that\u0027ll make my ships less deadly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wumpus","CreatedById":133850,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T16:43:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m assuming that tourists still can\u0027t EVA and are doomed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-01T20:45:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223341707\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522601034\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022133850\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wumpus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, wumpus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m assuming that tourists still can\u0027t EVA and are doomed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCorrect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-02T03:54:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223341676\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522599138\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187421\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lego_Prodigy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Lego_Prodigy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo how do I bail out both pilots with EVA chutes?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a part that attaches to the pod that ejects them.\u00A0 Check the mod thread for details.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}